jobInfo.postDescription:
Responsibilities:
As an engineer, you have the opportunity to work on the latest technology in big data area:
•	Design and develop world-class experience for new big data cloud offering
•	Design and implementation works from documentation, source code and production instrumentations
 
Qualifications:
•	Basic Qualifications:
o	BS degree in Computer Science/Engineering or with a similar major
o	1+ years of software design and development experience with at least one of C/C++/C#/Java/python/scala
o	Good writing, documentation, and communication skills in Engineering.
o	Familiar with IntelliJ and VSCode Extension
•	Preferred Qualifications:
o	Passion and experience for building great developer experience and user experience of modern analytics systems
o	Familiar with open source components like Spark and Hadoop ecosystem as a plus
o	Great curiosity and willingness to question
o	High enthusiasm, integrity, ingenuity, results-orientation, self-motivation, and resourcefulness in a fast-paced competitive environment
o	Have a deep desire to work collaboratively, solve problems with teams across the world, find win/win solutions and celebrate successes
o	Get excited by the challenge of hard technical problems
Solve problems by always leading with deep passion and empathy for customers

博彦科技（深交所上市公司, 股票代码002649）是亚太领先的全方位IT服务及行业解决方案提供商，具备全球范围内的交付能力。博彦科技创立于1995年，员工20000多人, 是中国IT行业的先行者和领军企业，拥有完善、成熟的管理和开发流程，确保为客户提供高质量的服务。公司全球总部设在北京中关村，在上海、深圳、广州、武汉、天津、西安、大连、成都已经设立研发中心，在美国硅谷、西雅图、洛杉矶，日本东京、新加坡、加拿大、印度、台湾、香港等国家和地区设立了全资子公司。博彦科技依托自身强大的研发与创新能力，广泛采用基于大数据，云计算和移动互联等新兴技术，为高科技、互联网、金融、汽车、能源、制造、医疗、电信、媒体、旅游等行业客户提供丰富的解决方案和产品。我们期待您的加盟，博彦会为您提供广阔的发展空间，提升自身价值的加速动力，热切欢迎有志之士！
